  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK24">
<l>uraṉeṉṉun tōṭṭiyā ṉōraintuṅ kāppāṉ</l>
<l>varaṉeṉṉum vaippukkōr vittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who restrains his five [senses] at once with the goad of firm [wisdom]</l>
<l>becomes one seed for planting [among those called] most high</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
